UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. Eugene L. COOPER, Appellee. No. 6474. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 25, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, it is ordered that the appeal herein be dismissed; mandate forthwith.
